}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"Celulitis","guid":"A-Z0cTKJQFGp-al5RiYM_g","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"DERMIS PROFUNDA + TCS","guid":"uol6iELST9yEvYTIGk3tnA","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Bordes DIFUSOS (vs erisipela)","guid":"mCIz8gZGQyaiUx3jyLXuVQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"Purulenta vs No purulenta","guid":"NyBdKLgXT-m17h4f6fjqCw","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"No purulenta → Streptococcus (cubrir)","guid":"tKMbSBkFScOX7e2EqmTOZg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"Purulenta → S. aureus incluyendo MRSA (cubrir)","guid":"5BkVokVyTWmb8cd866fGXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"121","text":"Clínica","guid":"0Nn1y-2sQ_iMhI6HUFjIeQ","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Eritema + calor + edema + dolor","guid":"3sxMKWjHR6iWPtz1Hl_GLw","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Sin bordes netos","guid":"nLQdyhiqRJ6C4oS71DWIWg","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Puede asociar linfangitis proximal","guid":"OdovGeF2SSKkpzJWU15iUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"121","text":"Diagnóstico\\NCLÍNICO","guid":"t6xsOxF5RSm382ZFPqvapQ","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Hemocultivos bajo rendimiento → solo si severa o inmunocomprometido","guid":"H9DL41hBSlSBf3sqFFiVoQ","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Imagen → solo si sospecha absceso oculto (ECO) o FN (TC)","guid":"53wfjpLkSTqRnHzRk-JS0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"121","text":"Mimickers (PSEUDOCELULITIS)\\N→ hasta 30%","guid":"JKJnzYu0RXylCUiLoVSpZA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"Dermatitis de estasis → bilateral, crónica","guid":"He044iUCR_aXOQaGDc3JQA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"Eczema/dermatitis contacto","guid":"cQOBNotdSAKuof1tbPB5_A","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"Linfedema","guid":"sY9O-tdFTQ270sDk0h7stA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"Eritema migrans (Lyme)","guid":"ebX3I6-fRAiIc7OpxeMzNw","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"134","text":"TVP","guid":"wJfQKNxHTRS1eF1doFoaSg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"134","text":"Gota aguda periarticular","guid":"DJQs6qS1QFSi_cibhVOQ-Q","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"134","text":"Score ALT-70 → predice celulitis verdadera extremidad inferior","guid":"1Ofrlwe9R2W4222N7WSMKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"121","text":"Tratamiento ambulatorio\\N(Leve, sin FR)","guid":"D53YZclmQzOH5t2yQuzp_Q","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"NO purulenta → Cefalexina 500mg c/6h o Amoxicilina x 5-7d","guid":"0QCPVcjoS3Kn9fQD877mqQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Purulenta → Cefalexina + TMP-SMX/Doxiciclina (cubrir MRSA)","guid":"8El3y5sIQNmb4nkrs8asyg","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Duración 5-7d suele bastar → NO prolongar rutinariamente","guid":"iEyD2N9HRXWMScNG3gsUgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"121","text":"Tratamiento hospitalario (Moderada-Severa)","guid":"E3HxmnikTfedhv4AaUBNbg","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"Cefazolina 1-2g c/8h EV","guid":"Ojmizb2ERzSU6zFg82qaqg","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Oxacilina/Cloxacilina 2g c/4-6h EV","guid":"-St9ZOuWQ4S-k7dC8fs67g","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"FR MRSA → Vancomicina 15-20 mg/kg c/8-12h o Daptomicina 6 mg/kg/d","guid":"FW4rqKHMQAiS3weOrlq_ug","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"146","text":"Alternativas → Linezolid, Ceftarolina, Dalbavancina, Oritavancina","guid":"zUq6hvGtRTmMNh5kRr2pKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"121","text":"Elevación + hidratación + marcar bordes","guid":"3I1MfZVyRtGFCPBmdrQJ1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Absceso\\NCutáneo","guid":"-2fttV3FRuapZSeeARwd2g","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Colección purulenta LOCALIZADA","guid":"wXuEzOl4R2OjpVXpfQLTuA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"S. aureus (considerar MRSA SIEMPRE)","guid":"mEnp9ebXSkuQwjU8qfRsng","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Clínica → nódulo fluctuante doloroso eritematoso","guid":"duOyyyHyRyWuln856X0jHw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Ecografía → confirma colección y guía drenaje","guid":"zuMr3uCtT7G7PSZazoNRbg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"TRATAMIENTO CENTRAL → I&D","guid":"n-xEzcXzQMyvkvOhaLmqRQ","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Loop drainage (drenaje en asa) → preferido sobre I&D clásica","guid":"mvB-BskCRICIwA839hqXUA","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Menos cicatriz, menos recurrencia","guid":"J6n6RWFPTrybU6NoCpOS2w","children":[]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"152","text":"ATB sistémico INDICADO si","guid":"283KoUeoSQKsc5-M7S_5CQ","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"Absceso >5cm (2cm en guías antiguas)","guid":"RFlkTde4TlG5FKMhGCr_Tw","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"Celulitis peri-lesional extensa","guid":"nDokvKuBTXyoVaFkPLf6lQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"Signos sistémicos / SIRS","guid":"8mtxlD7NTeGRvcpIoKNIAA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"160","text":"Inmunocomprometido","guid":"OXIwyPT3QTOiJvG45xVYpw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"160","text":"Extremos de edad","guid":"b7_kJWZqTrqFLWrjno5bEQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"160","text":"Cara, manos, periné (zonas alto riesgo)","guid":"z_hzLc5xRX2LBQcnzywGSA","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"160","text":"Drenaje incompleto o fracaso I&D previo","guid":"rXRq0X7EStaq5CbRCXUybg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"160","text":"Múltiples abscesos","guid":"Ka70BYn1QOe9pRxndAZ8Cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"152","text":"ATB empírico → cubrir MRSA","guid":"91XQtnV_RMqfHGi4SghbVw","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"TMP-SMX 160/800 c/12h VO","guid":"YKjPv1B3Q-SiBSeWXoexYw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"Clindamicina 300-450mg c/8h VO (cuidado C. difficile en AM)","guid":"ilhPMiwQSvK99et4wzXeeg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"Doxiciclina 100mg c/12h VO","guid":"bUxMdM-0TPaZ1UoIp3LKOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"152","text":"DEBATE → ATB post-I&D rutinario","guid":"62c-F70tTDifsAuhAxIKbw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Ensayos (Talan 2016, Daum 2017) → ATB mejora cura a 7-14d","guid":"tG9uAY2IR96BZvB-JS3AVA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Aún así I&D SOLO es opción en absceso simple no complicado","guid":"BTkQ0j89RGOcoLkVNAqSCg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Ectima","guid":"FypQ6AVjT2mZTJbdlX9wpg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Forma ULCERADA del impétigo","guid":"h2HM_WY0R7-2OF-Fgu4IRw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Compromete dermis → cicatriza","guid":"r8KdiiK4R5iqjzEzJ8TN7Q","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"S. pyogenes +/- S. aureus","guid":"08PMkfJnSfeias6hmJXe4Q","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"Úlcera \"en sacabocados\" con costra adherente","guid":"4M2jrD2yRaGfdqDVzUHupQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"Tratamiento → ATB sistémico (similar impétigo extenso)","guid":"7dYFnR8TRFStU0jA4wQlPg","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"176","text":"ECTIMA GANGRENOSO (distinto) → Pseudomonas en inmunocomprometido → NO es partes blandas superficial típica","guid":"9gtnL_2_R2iS3evuZ2Bghg","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"Hidrosadenitis Supurativa","guid":"lNZM9YGbTsq3KIPI8lSWlw","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Glándula apocrina → axila, inglé, perineo","guid":"E66su0f8R5moAt-9tgFVLg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"Enfermedad CRÓNICA inflamatoria (no solo infecciosa)","guid":"d4lEaufLSEC2QLo97UAUKA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"Nódulos recurrentes + trayectos fistulosos + cicatrices","guid":"i35VSRESSIaVc0-bOW4xgQ","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"Etiología multifactorial → genética, tabaco, obesidad","guid":"MhdY3lzcRyeVsY6ecrrIMA","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"Infección secundaria → S. aureus, anaerobios","guid":"Ivn9GOOhRc6uRzf7hA1rjw","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"183","text":"Manejo multimodal → ATB prolongados (clindamicina+rifampicina), adalimumab, cirugía","guid":"8kBfb_MbS-6WMczu7WuktA","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"0","text":"Linfangitis","guid":"z7AxlkrLSf66QRphPaI8zg","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"Inflamación vasos linfáticos subcutáneos","guid":"OXHtBr7URKSZ-6DXfl8TnQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"Clínica → líneas eritematosas ascendentes","guid":"IAQcysmcQYChZKqy1FZcIg","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"Adenopatía regional dolorosa","guid":"nihc7-lnSqWLTxnXSlW_dw","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"S. pyogenes principalmente","guid":"k5vb5DljS_moFKGWPQLroA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"Tratamiento → igual erisipela (penicilina/amoxicilina)","guid":"FZnJJqhOTL6DCuZY8MBVUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"Paroniquia","guid":"WNFGssX5QZyW1eAoKROgvA","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Infección peri-ungueal","guid":"3m0uicKNSemTWqUcRWI6HQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"AGUDA → S. aureus; trauma, manicura","guid":"0KHYf5l8SS-M5NHm6Cd-qA","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"Tto → calor húmedo + drenaje si colección + ATB si celulitis","guid":"Ia8cGasHRI-U1Sj6ZZzaAA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"Cefalexina / Amoxi-clav","guid":"IYKMw1e9QRyBLixYhs4niA","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","text":"CRÓNICA → Candida; humedad persistente, DM","guid":"-gQSPHKDQTSxtjp8Bacl-w","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Tto → antifúngico tópico + evitar humedad","guid":"esXhDO4JSYeosvjIbsveUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones Geriátricas","guid":"RPcogs2PRRuJm7IdNKtv9Q","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"PRESENTACIÓN ATÍPICA","guid":"1vYYmNodQLygt6aTjoZQOg","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"Fiebre ausente o leve","guid":"Mf6B4ZdPS9yq0qIf7QQxRA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"Eritema/calor reducidos → mala vascularización","guid":"gcKc0gS2RDi0crhQkQbTnw","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"PCR poco elevada → inmunosenescencia","guid":"1C3ZaO1dT_Sy2XGT_lX8Lg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"CONFUSIÓN / delirium → puede ser única manifestación","guid":"FZ2R5FfaR_ahMQH2mjJf8Q","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"204","text":"Cambio funcional / caídas","guid":"xkU033nIRgG-gZBzCKPOCw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"204","text":"NO descartar IPPB solo por ausencia signos clásicos","guid":"L74IoO0sSKGv7euH2yLcHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"203","text":"FACTORES RIESGO PECULIARES","guid":"-HxFzTXkQXCwMzI-MRCFBQ","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"Atrofia dérmica + fragilidad cutánea","guid":"0LcLMkZZSE-E6sVuLQgJyg","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"Inmunosenescencia","guid":"1AT5CAMNQGKMQyNPBIMiAQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"Edema crónico (IC, IVC, linfedema) → PUERTA persistente","guid":"1eDUiIlpT72D6EanUMHiPA","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"DM → x4 riesgo complicaciones cutáneas","guid":"YPIqVu0rReCMDEumxEl1EA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"Malnutrición → empeora pronóstico","guid":"MUb2GzcLS7WDHyaHN7VQUQ","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"211","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"iRMKPUNXTEG6D383I1oq8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"203","text":"DIAGNÓSTICO DIFERENCIAL CLAVE","guid":"d_Xt7AdgQ76d_AoGd0RWGg","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"Dermatitis estasis bilateral ≠ celulitis","guid":"aklm656vRj6NhB9S-BAnjg","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"NO tratar ambas piernas con ATB → repensar dx","guid":"CcLuYBfSSIaJZ_dFJIdO9Q","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"Hasta 30% celulitis mal diagnosticadas","guid":"0Bwxm-ILTE-pIJJ67WIE0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"203","text":"AJUSTE FARMACOLÓGICO","guid":"lQvNkQAoQmqUM8dGVwPQUQ","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"Dosis según ClCr (CKD-EPI)","guid":"WdoIITiTTGqUag0L5u3prw","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"Evitar/ajustar nefrotóxicos → vancomicina","guid":"qmnC4ypYSmSZD_hUUDuynQ","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"FLUOROQUINOLONAS → evitar si posible","guid":"GWH4mq0tRBWX43y9ADsvEg","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"QT prolongado, delirium, disección aórtica, tendinopatía","guid":"h7o-54DUQyCNDUuz_AVFCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"LINEZOLID → trombocitopenia, serotoninérgico (SSRI)","guid":"cU5NwlvST0GwMKllwYyOWA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"222","text":"CLINDAMICINA → C. difficile ↑ en AM → vigilar","guid":"AwRfF2YtRPeBQTdGht-HtQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"222","text":"DAPTOMICINA → rabdomiólisis, control CK","guid":"pKAP_WoWR8y6aMvUiQIV9Q","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"222","text":"Ajustar TMP-SMX → hiperK, ERC, warfarina","guid":"6UWEbihRS1-qgovFNH4viQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"203","text":"LIPOGLICOPÉPTIDOS LARGA DURACIÓN","guid":"CdCn3wyfQrKD5gL6VfX6XQ","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"DALBAVANCINA → 1500mg EV dosis única o 1000+500 semanal","guid":"60zmgDiYT7OlFo6FOvOMAw","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"Cubre MSSA, MRSA, Streptococos","guid":"s-JI98zkToyNGXmE_-EHdA","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"Evita hospitalización / permite alta precoz","guid":"53rCc2TLSzqXLEeanwY6qw","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"232","text":"Ideal en polifarmacia (no interacciones mayores)","guid":"LappOjRNQPKlvnuC8_Qvcg","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"232","text":"Requiere seguimiento clínico post-dosis","guid":"DyDhoPdCRwGs04rmeIM-PQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"231","text":"ORITAVANCINA → 1200mg EV dosis única","guid":"eq73ZZ68TS-1QtnMGA2rEw","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"231","text":"Ambos útiles en residentes de ELEAM","guid":"4wyJqrvbRaiCM9h-E-az4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"203","text":"OBJETIVOS TERAPÉUTICOS","guid":"w_pQuDYeSb6nRpQxw4wbAw","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"Curar + SEGURIDAD + alta precoz","guid":"OhvyenCNSBSmcT5YCgRZwQ","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"Terapia corta → menos EA, menos resistencia","guid":"hY3xINpGQbO-PMtq3ctMYw","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"239","text":"Switch IV a VO precoz si estabilidad","guid":"bA6x4ntxSsWm4-Ps1p0LIQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"239","text":"Evitar sobretratamiento (úlceras colonizadas vs infectadas)","guid":"VpGUUc5qQ9GqGkxOn2XNXQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"0","text":"Puntos de Alarma","guid":"R6dKMcnDQdKNOR8HyxEqfw","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"DOLOR DESPROPORCIONADO a signos cutáneos","guid":"BZZ7xgIUQfOrLbu6iJ432Q","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"Progresión >1cm/hora del eritema","guid":"1pKE5ILETTGJGvp2js6KuQ","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"Flictenas hemorrágicas / piel violácea","guid":"mq5kutAZRbOKiqOgG3MYkA","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"244","text":"Hipoestesia del área afectada","guid":"XhVu8skQQIO2wMfzpsD2iQ","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"244","text":"Crepitación","guid":"pXUWvj5VQjWaSI8_ig2Sqg","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"244","text":"TOXICIDAD sistémica desproporcionada","guid":"7SXHovQIQeK-0dQ9lETSCA","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"244","text":"→ Todo esto sugiere FASCITIS NECROTIZANTE","guid":"lL-CRWB9R2OtaJB2znp-EQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"244","text":"→ NO es partes blandas superficial","guid":"8vFVwRhSSbmnl8Bup8atGw","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"244","text":"→ Emergencia Qx, TC o exploración Qx INMEDIATA","guid":"WguQC3U9RyKJ5zb__HtpwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"G6wq3Uh2TxqGrVMOQc6sAA","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"Celulitis BILATERAL simultánea → casi SIEMPRE pseudocelulitis (estasis)","guid":"XpX_OCUxQ5urjpAbhKkE0A","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"Hemocultivos bajo rendimiento → reservar para severos/inmunocomprometidos","guid":"8aYKQxwwQaS_zQ-1MnCEqw","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"Elevar extremidad = tan importante como el ATB en erisipela","guid":"MICpr8LVQMawg6gFOZ9lyg","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"254","text":"Tratar tiña pedis = prevenir recurrencia de erisipela","guid":"ZSFXxnJaQYmsZOT9Qu2FFw","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"254","text":"Absceso simple <5cm → I&D sola puede bastar si paciente sano","guid":"Yq5g_H5MSkS-r-uiUc3YVw","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"254","text":"Loop drainage > I&D clásica en abscesos simples","guid":"_eWEy9ASSc6Kwrkc3__pKg","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"254","text":"En AM confusión nueva + eritema piel → descartar IPPB","guid":"xjPy0jOBRsuCOBgwrbwIhw","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"254","text":"PCR y fiebre normales NO descartan IPPB en adulto mayor","guid":"o-gwxmHCSomPyIlh52b58Q","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"254","text":"PATCH trial → Penicilina V profiláctica reduce recurrencia celulitis 45% (HR 0.55)","guid":"zeHl56ftQM2k0WLpCiJATw","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"254","text":"NO tratar colonización de úlcera → reservar ATB para infección clínica","guid":"DeasnGFmTISqW9VEfEGPvA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"254","text":"Dalbavancina dosis única útil en ELEAM para evitar hospitalización","guid":"r2yAtWZCQRGBp8znL1QiOA","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"254","text":"Marcar bordes del eritema al ingreso → objetivar respuesta a 48-72h","guid":"nxzaDrgaT-u36RjQC97vxg","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"254","text":"Respuesta clínica tarda 48-72h → NO cambiar ATB antes si no empeora","guid":"Gr74o_t4TLiP39W6YNs1qg","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"254","text":"Clindamicina AGREGA cobertura anti-toxina → considerar si extenso","guid":"h_NtrGNSRky-WP1yss-iyg","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"BqzC-Ie-R8Ku5Pvz-de9hQ","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"1. Stevens DL, Bisno AL, Chambers HF, et al. Practice Guidelines for the Diagnosis and Management of Skin and Soft Tissue Infections: 2014 Update by the IDSA. Clin Infect Dis. 2014;59(2):e10-52.","guid":"mVHydOhqQPy5Oa3-doYNRA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"2. Boettler MA, Kaffenberger BH, Chung CG. Cellulitis: A Review of Current Practice Guidelines and Differentiation from Pseudocellulitis. Am J Clin Dermatol. 2022;23(2):153-165.","guid":"-rBujqHARhWlrTUryYfipw","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"3. Long B, Gottlieb M. Diagnosis and Management of Cellulitis and Abscess in the Emergency Department Setting: An Evidence-Based Review. J Emerg Med. 2022;62(1):16-27.","guid":"u5qu26MKTSug4EfLwW6e6w","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"269","text":"4. Peghin M, Graziano E, Rovelli C, Grossi PA. Prevention and treatment of recurrent cellulitis. Curr Opin Infect Dis. 2023;36(2):95-101.","guid":"F7AJg6KzTwCyDDv19v-EVQ","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"269","text":"5. Hartman-Adams H, Banvard C, Juckett G. Impetigo: diagnosis and treatment. Am Fam Physician. 2014;90(4):229-235.","guid":"a7oU_G03QMGIVtjgspDKwA","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"269","text":"6. Esposito S, Bassetti M, Concia E, et al. Diagnosis and management of skin and soft-tissue infections (SSTI): a literature review and consensus statement. J Chemother. 2017;29(4):197-214.","guid":"537JS_G3T5SjJB1hsZ1beQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"269","text":"7. Sartelli M, Coccolini F, Kluger Y, et al. WSES/GAIS/WSIS/SIS-E/AAST global clinical pathways for patients with skin and soft tissue infections. World J Emerg Surg. 2022;17(1):3.","guid":"fQ-QY5uMQ--woYAbj-Bn_g","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"269","tex